message.text:
Hi ✨ is it okay if I ask for bag recommendations? I love my backpack, but I'm thinking of having a tote bag that could fit my laptop, laptop charger, and container that holds documents and yellow pads

I was thinking of buying the Bagsmart tote bag, but I was wondering if there are other options. Thank you for reading this and have a nice day ✨

The proclamation will meet the constitutional requirement that 20 percent of the House of Representatives consist of party-list representatives.

message.text:

The proclamation will meet the constitutional requirement that 20 percent of the House of Representatives consist of party-list representatives.
